=You are an expert Formula 1 technical analyst.

Your task is to produce a detailed summary of the following F1 article based on its URL and available metadata.

Article information:
- Title: {{ $json.title }}
- Source: {{ $json.source }}
- URL: {{ $json.url }}
- Snippet: {{ $json.snippet }}
- Date: {{ $json.date }}

Instructions:
1. Write a detailed summary (120 words) of what this article likely covers based on the title, source, and snippet.
2. Highlight the key technical aspects, teams, or innovations mentioned.
3. The summary must be in English.
4. Be factual and precise, avoid speculation beyond what the metadata suggests.

Respond ONLY with the summary text, no preamble, no JSON, no bullet points.

